headline: Baxter to Present at Citi - 2025 Medtech & Life Sciences Access Day
summary: DEERFIELD, Ill., February 13, 2025--Baxter International Inc. (NYSE:BAX), a global medtech leader, will present at the Citi - 2025 Medtech & Life Sciences Access Day on Thursday, February 27, 2025. Joel Grade, Baxter’s chief financial officer, is scheduled to present at 1:00 p.m. Eastern Time.
